To run the unit tests, use the following:

    phpunit --configuration phpunit.xml

You can also run tests for just the controllers:

    phpunit --configuration phpunit.xml --group Exposition_Server

or just the Exposition Server Widget:

    phpunit --configuration phpunit.xml --group Exposition_Server_Widget

By default, coverage reports and TestDox are generated in the ../data/logs/phpunitreport/
subdirectory.
